Key:21
I get 2 from History and 1 from Evolution in problem file.
You can easily decrypt using below code, this code is for encyption and decryption also.
So you have to give negative value for decryption and positive value for encryption.
Like in this question we have key 21 and we have to decrypt so we give -21 as a shift value.




#Code
print("Enter the word to be deciphered = ")
lines = []
while True:
    line = input()
    if line:
        lines.append(line)
    else:
        break
b = '\n'.join(lines)
shift=int(input("Enter shift value="))
l1=[]
l2=[]
for i in b:
    l1.append(ord(i))
for x in l1:
    if 64<x<91:
        if x+shift >90:
            x=x+shift-26
            l2.append(x)
        elif x+shift<65:
            x = x + shift + 26
            l2.append(x)
        else:
            l2.append(x+shift)
    elif 96<x<123:
        if x+shift >122:
            x=x+shift-26
            l2.append(x)
        elif x+shift<97:
            x = x + shift + 26
            l2.append(x)
        else:
            l2.append(x+shift)
    else:
        l2.append(x)
for c in l2:
    print(chr(c),end="")

